{"tid":1383223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黐飯食，好過份？","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:07:54.000Z","uid":260988,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f23a9e07af11adff54a30cbf7d5888a3fd14266d","tid":1383223,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:54:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我知好多窮苦學生，佢哋自己會心諗「<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>黐飯食好過份</strong></span>」<br />\n要幫佢哋<span style=\"color: orange;\">打破心理障礙</span>，就要<span style=\"color: orange;\">公平對待</span>，等佢哋覺得唔係白白伸手，所以，我諗到個<span style=\"color: orange;\">有尊嚴地分享美食</span>嘅方法，打破窮苦學生嘅心魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">《 連儂牆維護者招聘計劃 》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">只要post張相，證明清左連儂牆地下嘅垃圾，或者幫手執靚左一下連儂牆</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋有能力嘅就為付出左勞力嘅年青人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">等價交換</span></span>請返佢<span style=\"color: red;\">食飯或買裝備</span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n贊同嘅，請正評幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋繼續喺以下個 post 到約飯：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人一齊食飯呀？[遍地開花］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382296</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他相關題目<br />\n<br />\n如果義士冇錢食飯 歡迎嚟錫克廟 有免費三餐食<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382123</a><br />\n<br />\n救命啊無錢食飯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382323</a><br />\n<br />\n痴線，冇＄食飯，睇到喊咗。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381532</a><br />\n<br />\n【可行？】HKTV MALL 助養衝衝仔計劃！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382358</a><br />\n<br />\n助食計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382575</a><br />\n<br />\n請問點樣可以直接課金畀啲後生仔？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381280</a><br />\n<br />\n［飯券義助］推到人道基金、文宣入黎！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382261</a><br />\n<br />\n想資助小朋友返學既同我入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382952</a><br />\n<br />\n邊位手足買物資買到冇飯食嘅唔該入一入嚟！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381959</a><br />\n<br />\n我警告你班細蚊仔唔好再覺得自己佔咗人便宜啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382375</a>"},{"pid":"7a6cc6fe0d613fc04669d4f60c6ae576cbfd1d50","tid":1383223,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b38afd70c074166c6d2562efe677349060c73dd6","tid":1383223,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3e36383f445c45f7ea3c2b9aa19792bd3a47027","tid":1383223,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:55:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"800d48ba1ecb05203e5017d5b4e5d37e3c2a0053","tid":1383223,"uid":278277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d8db0485fa087f2ad2d0f40f2911c1a44bd12c0","tid":1383223,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:56:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"493b66e570dac764bf2e3ee6a96d18adcd335636","tid":1383223,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"126702860bde7a4b52f2c43db8825b65925a90c7